# Generated app definitions live at the repo root and carry real secrets in
# cleartext (admin passwords, SECRET_KEYs of live installations). They are
# output, not source — `zimapp.py convert` reproduces them at any time.
# blueprints/ is NOT affected: that is the source these are generated from.
/*.yml
!zimapp-src.yml

__pycache__/
*.pyc
gen.log

# Internal handover notes: infrastructure details of the machine this was built
# on, plus a section describing what an unauthenticated caller can do with an
# exposed instance. Everything a user of this repo needs is in README.md.
STATUS.md

# Local Claude Code settings.
.claude/
